\paragraph{Step 1: Lorentz Boost in Terms of Rapidity.} Recall the standard Lorentz transformation using rapidity $\eta$:
\begin{equation}
\begin{pmatrix} t \\ x \end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix} \cosh\eta & \sinh\eta \\
