\subsubsection{Matrix Embedding and Inversion}

The transformation in matrix form is:

\begin{equation}
\begin{pmatrix} \tau \\ t_x \end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix} \cos\alpha & \beta\sin\alpha \\
